{"data":{"site":{"pathPrefix":"/gb-gatsby"},"summary":{"html":"<h1 id=\"summary\">Summary</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/\">Introduction</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/objectifs/\">Objectifs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/enseignant/\">Enseignant</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/calendrier/\">Contenu</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-01-syllabus/\">Semaine 01 - Syllabus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-02-installfest/\">Semaine 02 - Installfest et +</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-03-unix/\">Semaine 03 - UNIX</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-04-python-1/\">Semaine 04 - Python 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-05-python-2/\">Semaine 05 - Python 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-06-python-3/\">Semaine 06 - Python 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-07-python-4/\">Semaine 07 - Python 4</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-08-relache/\">Semaine 08 - Relâche</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-09-pandas-1/\">Semaine 09 - Pandas 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-10-pandas-2/\">Semaine 10 - Pandas 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-11-presentations-1/\">Semaine 11 - Présentations initiales</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-12-visualisation-1/\">Semaine 12 - Visualisation 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-13-visualisation-2/\">Semaine 13 - Visualisation 2 et SQL</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-14-tutorat/\">Semaine 14 - Tutorat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/semaine-15-presentations-2/\">Semaine 15 - Présentations finales</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/travaux/\">Travaux</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/tutoriels/\">Tutoriels</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/bibliographie/\">Bibliographie</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/annexes/\">Annexes</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/politiques-16-et-42/\">Politiques #16 et #42</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/reglement-18/\">Règlement #18</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/gb-gatsby/politique-23/\">Politique #23</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"markdownRemark":{"h1":[{"value":"Cours 12 - Visualisation 1"}],"h2":[],"html":"<h1 id=\"cours-12---visualisation-1\">Cours 12 - Visualisation 1</h1>\n<h3 id=\"27-mars-2019\">27 mars 2019</h3>\n<hr>\n<p>Dans la première moitié du cours, on va voir quelques principes de base en information graphique en se basant, entre autres, sur l’ouvrage ci-dessous :</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.thefunctionalart.com/p/the-truthful-art-book.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 311px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 128.61736334405145%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"truthfulart\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/gb-gatsby/static/f0e3b50957db8db9824b627df6a5e34b/e316f/truthfulart.jpeg\"\n        srcset=\"/gb-gatsby/static/f0e3b50957db8db9824b627df6a5e34b/e316f/truthfulart.jpeg 311w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 311px) 100vw, 311px\"\n      />\n  </span></a></p>\n<p>Dans la seconde moitié du cours, on abordera ensuite quelques outils simples de visualisation interactive, dont:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://infogr.am\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Infogr.am</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.datawrapper.de/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Datawrapper</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://plot.ly/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Plot.ly</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Puis, on va plonger dans Carto.</p>\n<p><span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Carto Logo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/gb-gatsby/static/4cadee56347e2f038f4dab655f2ba3ea/693d8/Carto_Logo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/gb-gatsby/static/4cadee56347e2f038f4dab655f2ba3ea/903e3/Carto_Logo.png 336w,\n/gb-gatsby/static/4cadee56347e2f038f4dab655f2ba3ea/693d8/Carto_Logo.png 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n  </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://carto.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Carto</em></a> est un outil extrêmement bien fait de cartographie interactive. Je m’en suis souvent servi dans le passé. Voyez quelques exemples sur deux des comptes qui j’y possède : <a href=\"https://jhroy.carto.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">celui-ci</a> et <a href=\"https://jeanhuguesroy.carto.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">celui-là</a>.</p>\n<hr>\n<h5 id=\"retour-au-calendrier\">Retour au <a href=\"/gb-gatsby/calendrier/\">calendrier</a></h5>","wordCount":{"paragraphs":10,"sentences":12,"words":90},"excerpt":"Cours 12 - Visualisation 1 27 mars 2019 Dans la première moitié du cours, on va voir quelques principes de base en information graphique en…","timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/semaine-12-visualisation-1/","pages":[{"href":"/","value":"Introduction"},{"href":"/objectifs/","value":"Objectifs"},{"href":"/enseignant/",